org.apache.olingo.server.api.deserializer.batch

Class ODataResponsePart

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.olingo.server.api.deserializer.batch.ODataResponsePart

  • public class ODataResponsePart
extends Object
    An ODataResponsePart represents a collection of ODataResponses. A list of ODataResponseParts can be combined by the BatchSerializer to a single OData batch response.
